og.images/a-new-five-year-survey-of-the-magellanic-clouds-will-answer-some-questions-about-our-neighbors.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Dec 2025 22:56:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2025/12/a-new-five-year-survey-of-the-magellanic-clouds-will-answer-some-questions-about-our-neighbors</guid></item></channel></rss>